{"tid":1803689,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"狗咬狗骨黑吃黑 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-12-30T11:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T11:35:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"91251c9ee2588c2587d0f18d4a7da28b5be38724","tid":1803689,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T11:34:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191229/20833248/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F20833248%2F&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=37b45cdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F20833248%2F&h=f1cec933\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191229/20833248/</a><br />\n<br />\n狗咬狗骨黑吃黑 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191229/large/1577526343_521a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191229%2Flarge%2F1577526343_521a.jpg&h=5880f8f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府連出3篇新聞稿為警暴護航，林鄭亦在其廢fb專頁批評海外傳媒「不實報導」、「別有用心」、「文宣炒作」──政治生涯完結淪為行屍走肉的妹仔，死剩把口，真是「唔化」。<br />\n<br />\n最有力的，是《華盛頓郵報》發表詳盡報導，稱取得過百頁警方武力指引等文件，並邀請9名國際專家，審視6月至11月65宗香港警察使用武力事件，指約七成都有違規──即使精密分析，掌權者自閉，不屑一顧，而香港市民認為：黑警暴虐眾目睽睽，應在90％以上，有10％只鏡頭拍不到或白警灰警「略不作為」，且為良知索性辭職。<br />\n<br />\n你看那瘋狂失控愈亂愈好的平安夜、聖誕夜、香港陷於一片白茫茫山埃催淚毒氣中。Boxing Day大埔超級城，突有大批手持伸縮警棍的黑衣蒙面卧底衝向群眾，引起混亂，抓捕多人，其間竟有至少2名黑衣人，衝出商場時，被躁狂防暴黑警捉手箍頸推撞埋牆，制服後方知「自己人捉自己人」，「兵賊難分」極度惹笑，當其上司指揮官陶輝亦在新城市廣場混亂中「中椒」，滿臉通紅，更加心涼，可見濫暴有證據，濫捕為呃OT，狗咬狗骨黑吃黑「抵死！」，細思亦為黑警可哀──看到監警會副主席的22歲幼女跳樓身亡「無可疑」事件了？你們明白什麼是報應嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"1b2f5a836dc64fe05ce8d50366727cf7b64a622f","tid":1803689,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T11:35:12.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功)</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fcontent%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_23%2FPetition_99604.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=2646697f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功)</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_10%2F_01%2FPetition_99914.nc.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=9a6cbf80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html</a></span><br />\n3. <ins>暫時最後一個</ins> deadline 1/1 <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要34000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkVQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=92d9fef8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ep